quotes.quote: Y’all is the best, most inclusive, second-person, plural pronoun in the English-speaking world.
quotes.author: Hannah Gadsby

quotes.quote: today a man on the street pointed to me & said ‘what the hell is that!?’ i wanted to turn around, tell him that i got this dress on sale & i got this body for free but you have been making me pay for both ever since.
quotes.author: Alok Vaid Menon

quotes.quote: We had better not enjoy the moment, but create the moment.
quotes.author: Ai Weiwei

quotes.quote: If I didn't define myself for myself, I would be crunched into other people's fantasies for me and eaten alive.
quotes.author: Audre Lorde

quotes.quote: Our greatest glory is not in never falling, but in rising everytime we fall.
quotes.author: Confucius

quotes.quote: Don't count the days, make the days count.
quotes.author: Muhammad Ali

quotes.quote: Not everything that is faced can be changed, but nothing can be changed until it is faced.
quotes.author: James Baldwin

quotes.quote: You know, failure hurts. Any kind of failure stings. If you live in the sting, you will undoubtedly fail. My way of getting past the sting is to say no, I’m just not going to let this get me down.
quotes.author: Sonia Sotomayor

quotes.quote: The here and now is all we have, and if we play it right it's all we'll need.
quotes.author: Ann Richards
